fii:workflow.fii:name: STG02-Export-PreStage
fii:workflow.fii:description: Workflow is used to export records that are marked as PENDING in UVA2_PRE_STAGE to generate their full stage record.

fii:property.fii:name: workflowDescription
fii:property.fii:value: Workflow is used to export records that are marked as PENDING in UVA2_PRE_STAGE to generate their full stage record.

fii:property.fii:name: successEmailBody
fii:property.fii:value:
New user accounts have been provisioned
##$BREAK## User ##$entryId## has been provisioned with e-mail address ##mail## EntryId = ##$entryId## Status: ##$entryStatusID## ##$entryStatus##

fii:property.fii:name: successEntryEmailBody
fii:property.fii:value:
Your new account is ready for use.
Your e-mail address is ##mail##
EntryId = ##$entryId## Status: ##$entryStatusID## ##$entryStatus##

fii:property.fii:name: taskEmailBody

fii:property.fii:name: SQL
fii:property.fii:value: Select UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.CREATE_DATE, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.OTHERKEY01, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.OTHERKEY02, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.OTHERKEY03, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.OTHERKEY04, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.OTHERKEY05, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.RECORD_ID, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.ROWID, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.SOURCE, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.SOURCE_PROFILE_ID, UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE.STATUS From UVAIAMSVC.UVA2_PRE_STAGE where UPPER(UVA2_PRE_STAGE.STATUS)=UPPER('##%SOA_Status_Pending##')
